reviewText: Turku's musicians are wonderful, and I love Sufi music.  But the dancers aren't the same of 1999's video.  They are not so good, not so experienced.

A wonderfully colorful concert with great live music and really inspiring dances that are fresh and lively. Check out this video for really fun, entertaining performances of Silk Road music and dance. Also check out Turku's other video and CDs. Highly recommended!
